$ Enterprise Data Integration

{ Informatica PowerCenter

  PowerCenter is an → development/Data/warehousing/ETL tool used to build enterprise data warehouses.

  Main components
    • client tools
    • server
    • repository server
    • repository

  *Work flow managers* create work flows.

  Work flows can be monitored in work flow monitors.

  A *mapping* defines how → development/Data flows and is transformed between source to target. Mappings are created in a *mapping designer*.

  Typical transformations are:
    • aggregation
    • filtering
    • joining

}

